OL,5, A company has offered to provide free  
OL,6, security for a South Yorkshire church  
OL,7, food and clothes bank which has been   
OL,8, repeatedly targeted by a thief.        
OL,10,FSt John The Evangelist Church in Balby,
OL,11,FDoncaster, has been targeted seven     
OL,12,Ftimes, with stained glass windows      
OL,13,Fsmashed to gain entry on each occasion.
OL,15,FCCTV shows the intruder rifling through
OL,16,Fdonations, which the church gives away 
OL,17,Fto those who require them.             
OL,19,FNow a Leeds-based firm has offered its 
OL,20,Fservices to act as a deterrent.        
